{"comments":"CSS Value Constants\n\nPre-defined CSSValue constants for common CSS keywords. These provide\ntype-safe access to CSS values without string literals.\n\n## Categories\n\n- **Display**: block, flex, grid, inline-block, etc.\n- **Position**: static, relative, absolute, fixed, sticky\n- **Flex**: row, column, flex-start, center, space-between, etc.\n- **Border**: solid, dashed, dotted, double\n- **Text**: left, right, center, uppercase, ellipsis, etc.\n- **Cursor**: pointer, default, move, grab, etc.\n- **Visibility**: visible, hidden, collapse\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Render.Style.Values as V\nimport Hydrogen.Render.Style.Properties as P\n\nmyStyle = P.display V.flexValue\n       <> P.justifyContent V.center\n       <> P.cursor V.cursorPointer\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"CSS display: block\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Style","Core"],"CSSValue"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[110,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Style/Values.purs","start":[110,1]},"title":"block"},{"children":[],"comments":"CSS display: inline-block\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Style","Core"],"CSSValue"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[114,24],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Style/Values.purs","start":[114,1]},"title":"inlineBlock"},{"children":[],"comments":"CSS display: inline-flex\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Style","Core"],"CSSValue"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[118,23],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Render/Style/Values.purs","start":[118,1]},"title":"inlineFlex"},{"children":[],"comments":"CSS display: flex\nNamed `flexValue` to avoid conflict with `flex` property function\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Ren